    	Please send us an email or leave a message in the xxx section of our forums if you experience any problems using RC.
    	All the best!
</p>
    <div style="margin-top:30px; padding:20px 0 10px; line-height:24px; border-top:1px #ccc solid;">This letter was sent by system, please do not write back.<br>
